normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420724a28a4fba39e69626de1776b804c1db8a13","tid":1393692,"uid":57526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:55:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8fce74e940018d29f5f603fe021a4933ca62ad0d","tid":1393692,"uid":136182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:58:55.000Z","msg":"直接問上司85會點處理 然後佢話會通知hr通知大家有罷工 可以自由選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直接啲叫埋其他department 罷工"},{"pid":"ec009f2bbe09991e2e126325365c0f6d1dbeb608","tid":1393692,"uid":205275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T01:55:08.000Z","msg":"九月yr 2 依家喺某非中資銀行既back office翻緊intern<br />\n收到風好多人罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}